ugp.org.InnerUI

Class Manager

  • java.lang.Object
    • ugp.org.InnerUI.Manager

  • public class Manager
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the most important class in this library. This is place where is handle/update all windows and stuff about it like update handlers or remove closed windows. This class contains one list that contains all windows and every new window will be automatically added in to it.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    PETO
